=============================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 104
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "subscribeResponse": {
        "duration": "P5Y",
        "subscriptionId": "REGEX([0-9a-f]{24})",
        "throttling": "PT5S"
    }
}


HTTP/1.1 200 OK
